Titolo: Valley of the Minotaur

Anno: 1983

Descrizione: Valley of the Minotaur is an interactive fiction game for the Apple II, Commodore PET, VIC-20, and Commodore 64  home computers. It was published by Softalk magazine under the Zeuss Scientific label  in 1983. Inspired by Greek mythology, the goal of the game is to collect a set of treasures.